channel.description:
[size=20pt]Beat Silab Client - Development Team[/size]
[b]Hello, I Am Paintball199. I am Against the Silabs Client and I Want to make a New Client Due to the Lag of it. I Cant do it alone, I Will need Some People who I can Trust. I Know what Im doing. Please Dont only look at this Topic but Comment. This is gonna be a Very Big Dev Team due to Hardcoding everything, since we dont have a Unpacker & Repacker. The Following People Who I can Trust :[/b] Hidendra - My Best friend :) <3 TeleNubby - Cause hes teh sex. Furkan - awesome Guy. Bloodbath Aka R1ch dud3 - He Asked me so much help with Java. I Helped him and Now he Trusts me. such a good guy :) AD LVL 7 - Very good Guy, And Very Good coder. Wolf ( Project16 Creator ) - Very Good coder, Meeted him on Uber Server 3.0. Such a Good guy. Legend Rene - Since he Sended me the B Scape Blitz, I trusted him XD. Pk3r Kyle - Good Guy + Creator of Project Satan v3. M,i,k,e - Dunno why. M,i,k,e needs a <3 cause he told me on msn.
[b]These People I trust are Very nice =p The Jobs List :
#1 - Items Coding[/b]

[ul][li][/li] [li][/li] [li][/li] [li][/li] [li][/li] [li][/li] [li][/li] [li][/li][/ul]
[b]Dont Flame please. I Dont accept People who cant Hardcode. Its an Mega goal, I need to Spend very much time to it.
Requirements : Item Hardcoding. NPC Hardcoding.[/b]
[b]Thank you for your Time.[/b]
